"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The tariffs target around 60 trading partners because they did not stop forced labor properly.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tariffs on Trading Partners\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los aranceles afectan a unos 60 socios comerciales porque no detuvieron el trabajo forzado correctamente.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Aranceles a Socios Comerciales\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The price of Brent crude oil went up by more than 6% on Thursday as the war in the Middle East gets worse.\",            \"english_title\": \"Oil Price Rises\",            \"translated_version\": \"El precio del petr\u00f3leo Brent subi\u00f3 m\u00e1s del 6% el jueves mientras la guerra en el Medio Oriente empeora.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Sube Precio del Petr\u00f3leo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"At least 12 babies have been trafficked from Indonesia to Singapore, but it is not clear what will happen to them.\",            \"english_title\": \"Babies Trafficked\",            \"translated_version\": \"Al menos 12 beb\u00e9s han sido traficados de Indonesia a Singapur, pero no est\u00e1 claro qu\u00e9 pasar\u00e1 con ellos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Beb\u00e9s Traficados\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president says that the important agreement to help Saudis develop nuclear energy depends on them joining the Abraham Accords.\",            \"english_title\": \"Nuclear Energy Agreement\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. dice que el acuerdo importante para ayudar a los saud\u00edes a desarrollar energ\u00eda nuclear depende de que se unan a los Acuerdos de Abraham.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Acuerdo de Energ\u00eda Nuclear\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Most of the people evacuated were tourists from campsites around Arcachon Bay in France's Gironde region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tourists Evacuated\",            \"translated_version\": \"La mayor\u00eda de las personas evacuadas eran turistas de campamentos alrededor de la Bah\u00eda de Arcachon en la regi\u00f3n de Gironda en Francia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Turistas Evacuados\"        }    ]}"